Part of the reason I updated my bios is that my USB drive was acting a bit weird
Moved it from the slots designated for BIOS stuff, but the BIOS was still able to pull the BIOS file from it's current slot, and the drive was hitching sometimes
So I've moved it as far away from those 2 slots as I can while still using USB 3.0.  Time will tell if this solves the problem.
